				This doesn't answer the original question, but maybe it will give somebody else some ideas.  I read somewhere that there is a blacksmith in the caves that has some information on the Xakra shield.  I decided to go have a look, so I cast Invisible on myself just to be safe (even though the things were green to me) and went looking.  I did find a Gor Taku blacksmith, but since I'm dubious to him, he pretty much told me where to go.<BR>
