This is pure speculation, but since the guy is Gor Taku, I'm assuming I have to raise my faction in order to buy/talk to him.  Which means that I have to kill Shak Dratha to do so.  The part that bothers me is that Ragnar said the Shak Dratha have know how to weave shadow silk, which sounds like it is needed.  So to even find out about the shield, I have to mess up my faction with the Shak Dratha, but then I have a feeling that I'll then need to improve my faction with them to find out about the shadow silk.<BR>
